{"tid":735612,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Music 美國用戶數量超越 Spotify","createTime":"2018-07-09T15:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T04:00:22.000Z","uid":5787,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2786ec802749443c1b1b6e757958a2a8a47f67","tid":735612,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:24:59.000Z","msg":"串流音樂服務日漸受用戶歡迎，後來者 Apple Music 在美國的用戶人數，近日已經超越「前輩」Spotify。外國傳媒報導指 Apple Music 和 Spotify 的美國用戶數量都超過 2,000 萬，不過 Apple Music 稍稍領先，但由於保密原因，爆料的業界人士並沒有透露兩家公司的具體用戶人數。<br />\n<br />\n今年 2 月《華爾街日報》曾經指 Apple Music 能夠在美國市場後來居上，原因之一是上客速度較 Spotify 快，Apple Music 的用戶增長率約為 5%，但 Spotify 則只有約 2%。當時《華爾街日報》估計 Apple Music 於美國市場，會在今年夏天超越最大競爭者 Spotify。增長速度跑贏 Spotify 的原因，部份和消費者手上的 Apple 產品數量越來越多有關，除了手機、平板和智能手錶，Apple 今年初還推出了智能揚聲器 HomePod。<br />\n<br />\nApple CEO 今年 5 月曾經提及，Apple Music 全球用戶數量，包括付費和免費用戶，已經突破 5,000 萬。至於 Spotify 的全球付費用戶，在今年 3 月底為 7,500 萬名，而包括免費用戶在內的全球活躍用戶則超過 1.7 億。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/07/apple-music-exceed-spotify-in-us-market/mobile-music/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2Fapple-music-exceed-spotify-in-us-market%2Fmobile-music%2F&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=eef2fd41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/07/apple-music-exceed-spotify-in-us-market/mobile-music/</a>"},{"pid":"b1bb888e7a0e3bff86c17c461ee530421421aa2c","tid":735612,"uid":65453,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣覺得apple music 好用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b172708ace99effe80a98d365275288e349fd4","tid":735612,"uid":8511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1bb888e7a0e3bff86c17c461ee530421421aa2c","tid":735612,"uid":65453,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣覺得apple music 好用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo